OL,3,CNottingham triple killer 'deserves to
OL,4,Cbe punished', says victims' families
OL,6,FThe sons of one of the three victims
OL,7,Fof said their father's killer
OL,8,F"deserves to be punished" as they
OL,9,Fwelcomed the decision to have his
OL,10,Fsentence reviewed.
OL,12,FValdo Calocane, 32, was for killing
OL,13,Fschool caretaker Ian Coates, 65, and
OL,14,Funiversity students Barnaby Webber and
OL,15,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar, both 19, in a
OL,16,Fspate of stabbings in Nottingham last
OL,17,FJune.
OL,19,FThe Attorney General Victoria Prentis
OL,20,Fannounced on Tuesday that for being
OL,21,F"unduly lenient".
