OL,4,Cbe punished', says victims' families
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News, James and Lee
OL,7,FCoates, Mr Coates' sons, described the
OL,8,Fnews as "actual justice".
OL,10,FThey said news of the review "shows
OL,11,Fthat there is some good happening",
OL,12,Fadding that "it's the first positive
OL,13,Fnews we've got out of this whole
OL,14,Fdebacle."
OL,16,FJames said: "(The review is) just
OL,17,Fsomething to look forward to,
OL,18,Fsomething that's showing us there's a
OL,19,Flittle bit of hope that some sort of
OL,20,Fjustice is going to be done.
