OL,6,F"And the we're starting to feel like
OL,7,Fthere is some accountability."
OL,9,FHis brother Lee added: "We feel like
OL,10,Four voices are being heard a little
OL,11,Fbit more, now. For months we were
OL,12,Fjust, sort of batted away, either from
OL,13,Fthe police or from the powers (that)
OL,14,Fbe. So yeah, it's good that, like
OL,15,FJames said, finally, hopefully, there
